<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/916> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #916" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 9.42.10; Diod. 20.73.1; Fast. Cap. ([- -] Tr[e]mulus; P. Corn[elius- -]); Chr. 354 (Tremulo et Arvina); Fast. Hyd. (Remulo et Albino), so also Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; Degrassi 38f., 111, 422f. Cornelius fought Samnites who had taken Calatia and Sora, Marcius the Hernici and Anagnini, over whom he celebrated a triumph, and the{166} Samnites (Liv. 9.43; Cic. Phil. 6.13; Act. Tr., Degrassi 70f., 542; Plin. NH 34.23; cf. Diod. 20.80.1-4; Grueber, CRRBM 2.277; Cesano, Stud. Num. 1.153f.). These Consuls too (see 307) were omitted by Piso (Liv. 9.44.3-4)." ;
	dprr:hasID 916 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/915> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #915" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "The name of Marcius is preserved entire in Act. Tr. On the filiation of Cornelius Arvina, see Act. Tr. on Cornelius Cossus Arvina, Cos. 343. The name is preserved almost entire in Fast. Cap. for 294, Censors." ;
	dprr:hasID 915 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1026> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1026" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Chr. 354 (Tremulo II et Arvina); Fast. Hyd. (Cremulo et Albino), so also Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod. (Q. Marcius et P. Cornelius); Degrassi 112, 428f." ;
	dprr:hasID 1026 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1025> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1025" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "On the name of Marcius, see Act. Tr. on 306; on that of Cornelius, Fast. Cap. on 294." ;
	dprr:hasID 1025 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10156> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10156" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/30> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Triumph de Anagnineis, Herniceisque. MRR I.165-6, Itgenshorst no. 84, Rich no. 84." ;
	dprr:hasID 10156 .
